lifestyle that Austin offers.', 'From inner city activities like live music, 9th street, SUP boards and shopping to lakeside luxuries like boating and water sports, I have seen it all.', 'Also, being a wife & mother of 3 has helped me discover the kid friendly side of Austin and surrounding areas.', 'I first received my Real Estate License in 2007 and love being able to help people, like you,
